Parliament, Tuesday, 15 October 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will tomorrow receive a briefing from the Department of Justice and Constitutional Development on its annual report for 2018/19.
	
	Details are as follows: 
	Date: Wednesday, 16 October 2019
	Time: 9.30 am
	Venue: Committee Room M514, Fifth Floor, Marks Building.
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES 
	
